  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add sliced shallots and cook until they are translucent.",
    "Add curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add fermented black beans, coconut milk, salt, and pepper, and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Cook rice noodles according to package instructions and shock in an ice bath.",
    "Add cooked noodles to the curry mixture and stir well.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
